{"an7.31:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 7.31 ","an7.31:0.2":"3. Vajjisattakavagga ","an7.31:0.3":"Parabhavasutta ","an7.31:1.1":"“Sattime, bhikkhave, upasakassa parabhava …pe… ","an7.31:1.2":"sattime, bhikkhave, upasakassa sambhava. ","an7.31:1.3":"Katame satta? ","an7.31:1.4":"Bhikkhudassanam na hapeti, ","an7.31:1.5":"saddhammassavanam nappamajjati, ","an7.31:1.6":"adhisile sikkhati, ","an7.31:1.7":"pasadabahulo hoti, ","an7.31:1.8":"bhikkhusu theresu ceva navesu ca majjhimesu ca anuparambhacitto dhammam sunati na randhagavesi, ","an7.31:1.9":"na ito bahiddha dakkhineyyam gavesati, ","an7.31:1.10":"idha ca pubbakaram karoti. ","an7.31:1.11":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta upasakassa sambhavati. ","an7.31:2.1":"Dassanam bhavitattanam, ","an7.31:2.2":"Yo hapeti upasako; ","an7.31:2.3":"Savananca ariyadhammanam, ","an7.31:2.4":"Adhisile na sikkhati. ","an7.31:3.1":"Appasado ca bhikkhusu, ","an7.31:3.2":"bhiyyo bhiyyo pavaddhati; ","an7.31:3.3":"Uparambhakacitto ca, ","an7.31:3.4":"saddhammam sotumicchati. ","an7.31:4.1":"Ito ca bahiddha annam, ","an7.31:4.2":"dakkhineyyam gavesati; ","an7.31:4.3":"Tattheva ca pubbakaram, ","an7.31:4.4":"yo karoti upasako. ","an7.31:5.1":"Ete kho parihaniye, ","an7.31:5.2":"satta dhamme sudesite; ","an7.31:5.3":"Upasako sevamano, ","an7.31:5.4":"saddhamma parihayati. ","an7.31:6.1":"Dassanam bhavitattanam, ","an7.31:6.2":"Yo na hapeti upasako; ","an7.31:6.3":"Savananca ariyadhammanam, ","an7.31:6.4":"Adhisile ca sikkhati. ","an7.31:7.1":"Pasado cassa bhikkhusu, ","an7.31:7.2":"bhiyyo bhiyyo pavaddhati; ","an7.31:7.3":"Anuparambhacitto ca, ","an7.31:7.4":"saddhammam sotumicchati. ","an7.31:8.1":"Na ito bahiddha annam, ","an7.31:8.2":"dakkhineyyam gavesati; ","an7.31:8.3":"Idheva ca pubbakaram, ","an7.31:8.4":"yo karoti upasako. ","an7.31:9.1":"Ete kho aparihaniye, ","an7.31:9.2":"Satta dhamme sudesite; ","an7.31:9.3":"Upasako sevamano, ","an7.31:9.4":"Saddhamma na parihayati”ti. ","an7.31:9.5":"Ekadasamam. ","an7.31:9.6":"Vajjisattakavaggo tatiyo. ","an7.31:10.0":"Tassuddanam ","an7.31:10.1":"Saranda vassakaro ca, ","an7.31:10.2":"tisattakani bhikkhuka; ","an7.31:10.3":"Bodhisanna dve ca hani, ","an7.31:10.4":"vipatti ca parabhavoti. "}